data.description: Welcome home to this stunning 2 bed 2 bath condo. Aesthetically pleasing  w/ open floor plan, gorgeous kitchen w/ updated cabinets, SS appliances-  modern paint & hardwoods throughout! Relax & enjoy light filled large windows & electric fireplace in your living room. Beautiful bedrooms with deck off  primary- 2 spacious bathrooms w/ 2 full showers in primary & tubs in both baths! Amenities include beautiful courtyard w/ grills & seating, a theater, workout rooms, & outdoor verandas. Secure building & great location close to many amenities, restaurants & coffee. A/C & W/D in unit. Secure garage w/ 2 assigned parking spaces & a storage unit. Urban living in the heart of vibrant Tacoma! SELLER HAS VA ASSUMABLE LOAN W/ VERY LOW INTEREST RATE!!
